To build on a Mac it is necessary to:

1. brew install llvm
2. To use the bundled libc++ please use the following LDFLAGS:
  export LDFLAGS="-L/opt/homebrew/opt/llvm/lib/c++ -L/opt/homebrew/opt/llvm/lib/unwind -lunwind"

3. 'export PATH="/opt/homebrew/opt/llvm/bin:$PATH"

4. python -m venv .venv
5. source .venv/bin/activate
6. pip install -r requirements.txt
